Add these two lines at the end of axiom-large.input

lib:LIB:=3Dlibrary "data.KAF"
lib.'proba:=3D proba;

There probably is a bug somewhere in AXIOM (that's always a safe bet!)

Then, in a clean session, say

lib:LIB:=3Dlibrary "data.KAF"
keys lib
proba:=3Dlib.'proba





